<plot>In January 2007, indigenous communities in Guatemala are forcibly evicted from their land by a Canadian mining company. Community members watch as their homes are burned to the ground, and a woman being evicted lashes out at the police and other officials for the illegality and injustice of the evictions.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?141468</url></doc>
